Package: spatialcompare
Type: Package
Title: Visual Tableau and Comparison of Spatial Features Preserving Accurate Spatial Dimensions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Toby Wilkinson
Maintainer: Toby Wilkinson <open@tobywilkinson.co.uk>
URL: https://tcwilkinson.github.io/spatialcompare, https://github.com/tcwilkinson/spatialcompare
Description: This package designed to facilitate the construction of infographic tableau of diverse spatial features side-by-side.
   The package aims to preserve the accurate spatial dimensions of the features while translating their spatial position to allow visual comparison. 
   Applications include visual comparison of the dimensions of modern or ancient cities, study regions or building sizes in two dimensional space. 
